S&I 04 U. Series: 'Structure & Infill' 4/4. 
Designed at: H=N BLOCK+A, an extension patch(Architecture Kit) for H=N BLOCK, enabling realtime collaborative design using an architectural kit of parts. This S&I Series: 'Structure & Infill', captures realtime human interaction and placement of parts on generative architectural geometry.
